
This app must be run once before broadcast intents will be delivered to its background service. This is an Android security feature.

Thereafter, including after reboots, it should not be necessary the run this app at all.

Broadcast intents received:

   org.zapto.smblott.intentradio.PLAY
   extras:
      url:URL (optional, default is BBC Radio 4)
      name:NAME (optional, default is URL)

   org.zapto.smblott.intentradio.STOP
   (no extras)

Broadcast intents emitted:

   org.zapto.smblott.intentradio.LOG
   extras:
      msg:MESSAGE

All extras are strings.
